{"tid":2319042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好好珍惜袁弓夷、何良懋、龔小夏 加 程翔呢個組合","createTime":"2020-12-09T23:14:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T10:00:21.000Z","uid":154486,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ee987fac4e17d11f79d7ec5c10661a362b4441aa","tid":2319042,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T23:14:54.000Z","msg":"呢三個人<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"blue\">一個中美通殺，同大公司打官司多過食飯既通訊業商人</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"green\">一個火紅年代人物，亞洲週刊前助理主責編輯、加拿大星島前總編</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">一個前美國之音中文部主任，前記者，社會學博士，三年困難時期兼文革倖存者</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>星期日仲加埋程翔數臭共產黨</strong><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n而家可以每日係網上免費Live聽到<br />\n無論佢地既論點如何<br />\n呢個咁有料既組合唔係必然，一定要好好珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01c82f27d89035c2b8814909f533f8991d029323","tid":2319042,"uid":228143,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T23:18:37.000Z","msg":"大紀袁？"},{"pid":"5fb1096a8a6ad9f8ba762b802db0b86553aba820","tid":2319042,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T23:19:32.000Z","msg":"何良懋唔係二打六黎<br />\n當年係國粹派人物<br />\n<br />\n呢篇文佢有講佢以前既經歷<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.thenewslens.com/article/126297\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F126297&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYpseYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=7efe147f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.thenewslens.com/article/126297</a>"},{"pid":"e7a025269fb9f1412cf65fdf643c156befc9f9d2","tid":2319042,"uid":91397,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T23:24:10.000Z","msg":"就係論點嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e02625c67d08ea0cd1287f74943b0f96b6528b4","tid":2319042,"uid":11097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01c82f27d89035c2b8814909f533f8991d029323","tid":2319042,"uid":228143,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2